  m_Name: Speech_MrAngerIssues_Ending
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::ClientSpeech
  Clip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: b1f38f10148a7de4da85b720fc4c02ce, type: 3}
  Subtitles: "Anyway, I think I might actually want to ask her out, seriously\u2026
    If only this GODDAMN FUCKING boss of mine gives me an actual damn vacation. How
    fucked am I if I can\u2019t even get the goddamn vehicles to move? I\u2019m a
    fucking mechanic by trade! Like Jesus fucking Christ I want to just throw the
    wrench at him, you know what I mean? Should I try giving her antifreeze, to tinker
    with?"
